DAZ Studio Type Definitions

There are a number of basic types that have been defined for use throughout DAZ Studio. These are outlined below. Click on the type name to go to a detailed description of the type.

  • typedef int DzTime
  • typedef float DzPnt2[2]
  • typedef float DzPnt3[3]
  • typedef unsigned int DzError
  • typedef float DzMat3 [4][3]
  • typedef float DzMatRow [3]
  • typedef float DzMat4 [4][4]
  • typedef int DzQuat::AxisOrder [3]
  • typedef enum en_DzLocation { DzTop, DzBottom, DzLeft, DzRight, DzCenter } DzLocation

There are also a number of predefined shared pointer types use in the DAZ Studio SDK. These handle referencing/dereferencing for ref-counted types in D|S.

  • typedef DzTSharedPointer<DzImage> DzImagePtr
  • typedef DzTSharedPointer<DzMap> DzMapPtr
  • typedef DzTSharedPointer<DzMaterial> DzMaterialPtr
  • typedef DzTSharedPointer<DzContentFile> DzContentFilePtr
  • typedef DzTSharedPointer<DzContentFolder> DzContentFolderPtr

DAZ Studio makes a lot of use of the QList template class. There are a number of predefined QList types and iterators for those types that you may run into while working with the DAZ Studio SDK.

  • typedef QListIterator<DzProperty *> DzPropertyListIterator
  • typedef QListIterator<DzActionMenuItem *> DzActionMenuIterator
  • typedef QListIterator<DzPane *> DzPaneListIterator
  • typedef QListIterator<DzPaneGroup *> DzPaneGroupListIterator
  • typedef QListIterator<DzClassFactory *> DzClassFactoryIterator
  • typedef QList<DzNode *> DzNodeList
  • typedef QListIterator<DzNode *> DzNodeListIterator
  • typedef QList<DzLight *> DzLightList
  • typedef QListIterator<DzLight *> DzLightListIterator
  • typedef QList<DzCamera *> DzCameraList
  • typedef QListIterator<DzCamera *> DzCameraListIterator
  • typedef QList<DzBone *> DzBoneList
  • typedef QListIterator<DzBone *> DzBoneListIterator
  • typedef QList<DzSkeleton *> DzSkeletonList
  • typedef QListIterator<DzSkeleton *> DzSkeletonListIterator
  • typedef QList<DzTimeRange> DzTimeRangeList
  • typedef QList<DzTimeRange>::iterator DzTimeRangeListIterator
  • typedef QList<DzWSModifier *> DzWSModifierList
  • typedef QListIterator<DzWSModifier *> DzWSModifierIterator

You may also run into some native array types as you work with the DAZ Studio SDK.

  • typedef DzTArray<DzMaterialPtr> DzMaterialPtrList
